🔷 8. Common Issues & Fixes
❌ Composer not found

✔ Fix:
Add to PATH:

C:\ProgramData\ComposerSetup\bin

❌ PHP not detected

✔ Fix:
Set PHP path manually during installation

❌ SSL error

✔ Fix:
Enable OpenSSL in php.ini

🔷 9. Real Use After Installation

You can now use:

composer init
composer install
composer require laravel/framework
composer update

⭐ Final Summary (Very Important)

👉 Composer is installed via official installer or package managers.
👉 It connects PHP projects to external libraries via Packagist.
👉 After installation, composer -V confirms setup.
